name: Warmup_Div03_Sub02
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD3S2.CPF,
GmailD3S2.NOME,
GmailD3S2.EMAIL,
GmailD3S2.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S2.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD3S2.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD3S2.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S2.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV03_SUB02 GmailD3S2
UNION
